item.title: Post Format Audio
item.dc:creator: materialize
item.content:encoded:
All children, except one, grow up. They soon know that they will grow up, and the way Wendy knew was this. One day when she was two years old she was playing in a garden, and she plucked another flower and ran with it to her mother. I suppose she must have looked rather delightful.<!--more-->
This was all that passed between them on the subject, but henceforth Wendy knew that she must grow up. You always know after you are two. Two is the beginning of the end.
Mrs. Darling first heard of Peter when she was tidying up her childrens minds. It is the nightly custom of every good mother after her children are asleep to rummage in their minds and put things straight for next morning, repacking into their proper places the many articles that have wandered during the day.

item.title: Senior UX/UI Designer
item.dc:creator: materialize
item.content:encoded:
Responsible for the Frontend Development and is motivated to combine programming and design, you working experience in Javascript and AngularJS is essential along with core skills in AJAX, HTML5 and CSS3. You will be a creative individual, being able to communicate new ideas to stakeholders and support a well-established and creative in house development team.  

No. of Vacancies

  • 02
 

The successful Front-End Developer will have skills in:

  1. Proficient understanding of web mark-up, including HTML5, CSS3
  2. Basic understanding of server-side CSS pre-processing platforms, such as SASS
  3. Proficient understanding of client-side scripting and JavaScript frameworks, including jQuery
  4. Good understanding of and knowledge of advanced JavaScript libraries and frameworks, such as AngularJS, ReactJS etc.
  5. Small adjustments on an image. Familiarity with tools such as Photoshop is a plus.
  6. Proficient understanding of cross-browser compatibility issues and ways to work around them.
  7. Proficient understanding of code versioning tools, such as GIT , SVN
  8. Basic knowledge of image authoring tools, to be able to crop, resize, or perform.
 

Desired Qualifications:

  1. Bachelors degree and/or equivalent experience in Web Systems Design
  2. 5+ years strong technical web development experience
  3. Language Knowledge - HTML, JavaScript, JQuery, AJAX, CSS3
  4. Strong interpersonal, written and oral skills.
  5. Python, Django or equivalent Web Development Framework experience using MVC Design Pattern
  6. Strong Unix and Oracle Database experience
  7. Good understanding of Accessibility and different level of compliance.
 

Job Nature

  • Full-time
 

Educational Requirements

  • Bachelor degree in computer science and engineering.
 

Experience Requirements

  • 1 to 2 year(s)
  • The applicants should have experience in the following area(s): System Engineer (Telecommunication Network), System Engineer (Computer Network & System)
  • The applicants should have experience in the following business area(s): Software Companies.
 

Salary Range

  • 40000/yearly
